] Copyright 2020, American Chemical Society. b) self‐heating rate from accelerated rate calorimetry (ARC) of LiFePO4/Li pouch cell with solid polymer electrolyte (polyether with LiTFSI) and c) with liquid carbonate‐based electrolyte at 50% and 100% state‐of‐charge. b,c) Reproduced with permission.[
