] Copyright 2020, Elsevier. c) schematic of high temperature Li‐O2 enabled by SSE and d) Gibbs free energy of reaction as a function of temperature, indicating the possibility of a four electron process at elevated temperature (≈150 °C). c,d) Reproduced with permission.[
